Deep scientific minds
but able to fly out there

00:23:04.640 --> 00:23:05.870 align:middle line:90%
as mystics as well.

00:23:05.870 --> 00:23:06.670 align:middle line:90%
>> MILLS: Yes.

00:23:06.670 --> 00:23:08.628 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And so Feynman,
let's talk about him

00:23:08.628 --> 00:23:11.000 align:middle line:84%
because he's commenting,
he's talking about religion

00:23:11.000 --> 00:23:14.540 align:middle line:84%
