I mean, the matter of a human
can fit on the pin of a head.

00:24:48.250 --> 00:24:50.120 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the head of
a pin, head of a pin.

00:24:50.120 --> 00:24:50.920 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:24:50.920 --> 00:24:52.420 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, pinhead.

00:24:52.420 --> 00:24:56.470 align:middle line:84%
I mean, so what is this
construct in front of us?

00:24:56.470 --> 00:25:02.020 align:middle line:84%
