Yeah, and I want
people, as this begins

00:26:37.362 --> 00:26:38.820 align:middle line:84%
to happen more and
more for people,

00:26:38.820 --> 00:26:41.280 align:middle line:84%
I want people to
have a confidence

00:26:41.280 --> 00:26:43.980 align:middle line:90%
to proceed and step forward.

